title: [DB] Naruto Shippuden Movie 2 (Bonds) [PSP, Ipod, Zune...)
description:
This is the second installment of the Shippuden Movie series.

It was first downloaded at Dattebayo and then converted into MP4 format which is compatible with PSP, Ipod, Zune, and Etc...

Same great quality!

Size is kind of big but lowering into a lower bitrate will kill the quality.

Hope you have a big memory.

Also the THM file is a thumbnail file to add a picture to the movie such as on a PSP Video menu. Just place it together with the MP4 file.

Enjoy!
